13:["$","p",null,{"children":"To create a recognizable brand that brings the heat. Designing packaging, menus, and marketing materials that reinforce the handcrafted, wood-fired experience. Establishing a strong digital presence, including social media visuals and a logo that feel cohesive and high-end."}]
14:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Logo Design"}]
15:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Using retro typography, the shape of a classic pizza oven, and flame inspiration, I created this logo family for this concept to make its mark.\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/1.png","alt":"The brand needed a capstone for thumbnails. By combining the fiery red that the brand uses to attract attention, set against a light tan for the main typography, it's subtle but warm.","caption":"The brand needed a capstone for thumbnails. By combining the fiery red that the brand uses to attract attention, set against a light tan for the main typography, it's subtle but warm.","zoom":true}],"\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/2.png","alt":"This image features the logo variations Fueco could use for everything from packaging to social media. These designs unite to create a comprehensive logo family.","caption":"This image features the logo variations Fueco could use for everything from packaging to social media. These designs unite to create a comprehensive logo family.","zoom":true}]]}]
16:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Color Palette"}]
17:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Fueco’s colors capture the heat and intensity of wood-fired pizza. Fiery Red and Ember evoke flames and passion, while Charcoal adds depth and smokiness. Ivory provides balance, ensuring clarity and sophistication. This palette reinforces Fueco’s bold, high-energy identity at every touchpoint.\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/3.png","alt":"In a stroke of creativity, matches were chosen to illustrate the brand's chosen color system. The flames are energetic and connect to the ethos of fire-baked pizza.","caption":"In a stroke of creativity, matches were chosen to illustrate the brand's chosen color system. The flames are energetic and connect to the ethos of fire-baked pizza.","zoom":true}]]}]
18:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Menu & Wine Packaging"}]
19:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["For this section, I wanted to really give the viewer a look into what it would be like to sit and sip a glass of wine at this cozy, Italian pizzeria. I used Photoshop to add in the menu design I created for the brand and added a subtle grain to give it an \"old world\" quality. This style can be reused for all the brand imagery.\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/4.png","alt":"In this image you will find a table setting that gives the brand a warm and homey feel. This was intentional. Adding the menu and wine list brought the idea together. This is what it would be enjoying your time at Fueco.","caption":"In this image you will find a table setting that gives the brand a warm and homey feel. This was intentional. Adding the menu and wine list brought the idea together. This is what it would be enjoying your time at Fueco.","zoom":true}],"\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/5.png","alt":"In this mock-up two wine bottles dance together on a deep red background. For the label design, I kept it simple using the dark background and linework to create a striking contrast.","caption":"In this mock-up two wine bottles dance together on a deep red background. For the label design, I kept it simple using the dark background and linework to create a striking contrast.","zoom":true}]]}]
1a:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Social Media"}]
1b:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Fueco’s social media design embraces high-contrast visuals, bold typography, and dynamic layouts to capture attention instantly. The mix of mouthwatering food photography, strong brand elements, and vibrant red accents ensures a cohesive, scroll-stopping presence. Every post reinforces Fueco’s fiery, fast-paced energy, making the brand impossible to ignore.\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/6.png","alt":"Alternating panels combine to provide a trendy look into the many working parts of a pizzeria. Elements of typography, custom patterns, product and lifestyle photography, and more give an energetic and cohesive vibe to their social media.","caption":"Alternating panels combine to provide a trendy look into the many working parts of a pizzeria. Elements of typography, custom patterns, product and lifestyle photography, and more give an energetic and cohesive vibe to their social media.","zoom":true}],"\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/8.png","alt":"In this picture, Instagram post mock-ups illustrate snapshots of product photography, logo design, packaging design, and lifestyle imagery.","caption":"In this picture, Instagram post mock-ups illustrate snapshots of product photography, logo design, packaging design, and lifestyle imagery.","zoom":true}]]}]
1c:["$","h2",null,{"children":"Basic Website/Application Design"}]
1d:["$","div",null,{"className":"my-4","children":["Although I didn't expand on this section of the project as much as I would have liked, I used a laptop outline to throw together a quick look at what the brand's website or pizza order app could look like. Emphasis on simple line art that adds structure without distracting from the main message: DELICIOUS PIZZA!\n",["$","$L20",null,{"src":"/work/fueco-pizza/7.png","alt":"I sourced some mouthwatering product photography for this section, and I think it brought the heat. Product photography is a must for any food/beverage branding.","caption":"I sourced some mouthwatering product photography for this section, and I think it brought the heat. Product photography is a must for any food/beverage branding.","zoom":true}]]}]
1e:["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-stroke pt-card","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/work/connect-social","className":"group","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-muted","children":"Previous project"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-base font-semibold text-white group-hover:underline","children":"Concept: Connect Social Technology"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-1 text-sm text-muted","children":"Brand design concept and marketing materials for Connect Social Technology: a social media company"}]]}],["$","$L12",null,{"href":"/work/whitmore","className":"group sm:text-right","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-muted","children":"Next project"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-base font-semibold text-white group-hover:underline","children":"Concept: Whitmore Real Estate"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-1 text-sm text-muted","children":"Logo, branding design and marketing materials for the concept: Whitmore Real Estate"}]]}]]}]}]
